{
  "title": "Savory Sweet Croatian Gouda Wrap",
  "description": "A crowd-pleasing Croatian dish featuring gouda cheese and a sweet glaze, wrapped in a corn husk wrap, perfect for a low-glycemic diet.",
  "cuisine": "Croatian",
  "diet": [
